This initial release of maia mailguard 1.0.4r targets centos 7.

To install on Centos/RHEL 7, simply run:

        install-centos7.sh

In general, there will be scripts for other distros such that one can say:

        install-<distro>.sh

Until your distro is listed, you may install manually

Note - It will take some time to complete, depending on bandwidth and CPU

